            "id": 5940511,
            "title": "大城小室空間設計—輕 淨",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>明亮純白的材質，寧靜而平和的氛圍，置身其間，猶如白紙使人擁有純淨的心，享受空間之中的純白時光。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>在空間中將喧囂輕輕的拂去，只留下最澄澈的部分——純粹、乾淨、靜美、簡單而不匱乏，給予人舒適、自由且靜謐中最恰好的温度。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮獲 2022 法國 NOVUM Design Awar 室內設計類 銀獎</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮獲 2022 美國 MUSE Design Awards 銀獎</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/e918f4c8f90beb40fd8ff62158332a7e.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/e918f4c8f90beb40fd8ff62158332a7e.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/efdc45289f3597c7399ceb1a47485859.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/efdc45289f3597c7399ceb1a47485859.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/b6bdc196e5b8ac1db350b6dc3abfdef9.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/b6bdc196e5b8ac1db350b6dc3abfdef9.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/c67819ddb6aaa59abe20402c668e6634.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/c67819ddb6aaa59abe20402c668e6634.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/0d418e4451224dcea8b759f4bee27b3d.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/0d418e4451224dcea8b759f4bee27b3d.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/1e81f9e89e5cb8ed1545e794174c1b03.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/1e81f9e89e5cb8ed1545e794174c1b03.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"1139\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.6672519754170325\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/200d5832a6cb633b87cc15ad1ed64ed5.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/200d5832a6cb633b87cc15ad1ed64ed5.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"506\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.5019762845849802\" data-src-m=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/m/859cf0b4fffdc2f05d6cca8cfb466785.jpg\" data-width=\"760\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/5940511/l/859cf0b4fffdc2f05d6cca8cfb466785.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-height=\"1140\" data-mime=\"image/jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-src-m=\"https: